Usage: set_power_include_file [-help] [<file>] [-block <string>] [-reset]

-help                           # Prints out the command usage
<file>                          # Specifies the powermeter include file which
                                # contains powermeter options (string, optional)
-block <string>                 # Specifies master cell name for the powermeter
                                # include file which contains powermeter
                                # options to be applied (string, optional)
-reset                          # Specifies to reset and ignore all the
                                # previous powermeter include files.
                                # (bool, optional)